{
  "id": "69e00995dacd452c2521e753",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:インポスター症候群",
  "created": 1776290220,
  "updated": 1776291885,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e00995dacd452c2521e753",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:インポスター症候群",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290220,
      "updated": 1776290220
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ac0000000000914a94",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290220,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a95",
      "text": "「はいどーも！本日のゆるっと鼎談テーマは〜『[インポスター症候群]』でーす！……って名前からしてラスボス感ない？なんか“正体不明の怪物”みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a97",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a98",
      "text": "「語感は確かにRPGの隠しボス。ただ実体は心理現象。自分の実力を過小評価して、“自分は偽物だ”と感じる状態を指す」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a99",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9b",
      "text": "「急にガチ解説きたｗ つまり“私なんてたまたまうまくいっただけで、本当はザコです…”みたいなやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9e",
      "text": "「ええ、そのような心持ちですわね。たとえ努力を重ねて得た成果であっても、それを自分のものとして受け取れず、偶然や周囲の好意に帰してしまう……心の奥で、自分を疑い続けてしまうのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914a9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa1",
      "text": "「うわ〜それ、テストでいい点とったときに“今回だけ運よかっただけっしょ”って思うやつじゃん。あるあるすぎて泣いた」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa4",
      "text": "「その認知の偏りには名前がある。インポスター症候群。研究としては1978年にClanceとImesが提唱。概要はこちら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa5",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impostor_syndrome 」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa8",
      "text": "「リンク貼るな貼るなｗ ここ論文発表の場じゃないのよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aa9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aaa",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aab",
      "text": "「エビデンスは心の安定剤。さて、要点を整理する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aac",
      "text": " 1. 成功を内的要因ではなく外的要因に帰属",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aad",
      "text": " 2. 失敗は自分の能力不足として強く記憶",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aae",
      "text": " 3. “いつかバレる”という不安を持つ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aaf",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab2",
      "text": "「うわ、チェックリストみたいに並べられると刺さるんだが？HP削られてる音する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab4",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab5",
      "text": "「そのお気持ち、とても自然なものだと思いますわ。誰しも、他者のまなざしの中で自分を測ってしまうことがありますもの。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab8",
      "text": "「やさしさが染みる…あや、ヒーラーじゃん」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ab9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aba",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914abb",
      "text": "「ただし、この状態は能力の有無とは相関が弱い。むしろ高い成果を出している人ほど感じやすいという報告もある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914abc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914abd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914abe",
      "text": "「え、なにそれ。“強キャラほど不安デバフ持ち”みたいな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914abf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac1",
      "text": "「表現は雑だが概ね正しい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0102000000000009c4da6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776291872,
      "updated": 1776291872
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776291885
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0102200000000009c4da7",
      "text": "「自らに課す理想が高いほど、現実の自分との距離を大きく感じてしまうのでしょうね。まるで、遠くに見える星を手に取ろうとするように」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776291874,
      "updated": 1776291874
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac5",
      "text": "「ポエムきた〜！でもわかる。理想の自分がSSRすぎて、現実の自分がノーマルカードに見えるやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac8",
      "text": "「その比喩、意外と有効。認知再構成としては“達成した事実をログとして保存する”のが一つの手法」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ac9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aca",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914acb",
      "text": "「ログってなに、ゲームのセーブデータ的な？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914acc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914acd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ace",
      "text": "「そう。たとえば“テストで80点を取った”という事実を、“運が良かった”ではなく“勉強した結果”として記録する。主観ではなく事実ベースで」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914acf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad1",
      "text": "「日記のように、自分の歩みを丁寧に書き留めるのも良さそうですわね。過去の自分が、今の自分をそっと支えてくれるようで」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad4",
      "text": "「なるほどな〜。“未来の自分への応援メッセージ”って感じか。エモい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad7",
      "text": "「もう一つ。“比較対象を適切に設定する”。SNSなどで上位層だけを見続けると、基準が歪む」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ad9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ada",
      "text": "「わかる〜！タイムラインって基本“神プレイ集”だからさ、自分が下手に見える罠よね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914adb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914adc",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914add",
      "text": "「他者は物語の一頁しか見せていないことも多いですものね。その裏にある努力や迷いは、なかなか見えないものです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ade",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914adf",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae0",
      "text": "「そう考えると、“自分だけがダメ”って思うの、ちょい早とちりかもな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae3",
      "text": "「その認識は妥当。要点をまとめる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae4",
      "text": " インポスター症候群は珍しくない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae5",
      "text": " 成功を適切に自分の成果として認識することが重要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae6",
      "text": " 比較の仕方を調整する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae7",
      "text": "この3点で、かなり見え方が変わる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914ae9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aea",
      "text": "「はい出ました、りかの“まとめ助かる”タイム」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aeb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aec",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aed",
      "text": "「自分を偽りだと思う気持ちがあったとしても、それはむしろ、誠実に物事と向き合っている証かもしれませんわね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aef",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af0",
      "text": "「それめっちゃいい解釈じゃん！“疑う＝ちゃんと考えてる人”ってことか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af3",
      "text": "「そういう視点も有効。自己評価はシステム。調整可能」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af6",
      "text": "「最後ちょっとロボっぽいんよｗ でもなんか元気出たわ。“私ザコかも…”って思っても、“いやログ見ろログ！”って言い返せばいいのね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914af9",
      "text": "「ええ、ご自身の歩みを信じて差し上げてくださいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914afa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914afb",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914afc",
      "text": "「そして定期的にバックアップを取ること。心のデータは消えやすい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914afd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914afe",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009ad0000000000914aff",
      "text": "「それはガチｗ メンタルのオートセーブ実装してくれ〜！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290221,
      "updated": 1776290221
    },
    {
      "id": "69e009f60000000000914b00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776290295,
      "updated": 1776290295
    },
